                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/aa84d77a03ee4e755a8df65d62146b13_7199952721509217005.png",
