              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8160589593284500515.png",
                "id": "talent7346",
                "key": "奥兹",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/6a5ec549833ce08e3439c207909b0bdb_6207596840480422437.png",
                "title": "奥兹"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7913026770578931945.png",
                "id": "talent3371",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p> </p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p> </p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4633866867623827949.png",
